snippet.title: Harley Quinn and Poison Ivy Sequel | Ezra Miller and Amber Heard Situation | Next Snyder Cut Event
snippet.description:
Harley Quinn and Poison Ivy Sequel | Ezra Miller and Amber Heard Situation | Next Snyder Cut Event

Cathy Yan talks about exploring Harley Quinn and Poison Ivy’s relationship in a potential sequel.
Viral video apparently shows Ezra Miller choke holding a woman.  How would this affect his future role as Flash?  Also discussing Amber Heard as Mera.

Welcome back to the Ping Pong Flix Show for all up to date DC Movie News, my name is Chris Wong-Swenson.  I'm a YouTube Journalist discussing, reporting, and speculating on all DCEU, DC Films, DC Animation, other DC Comics Entertainment content including movies, games and shows! Also an Associate Producer for Zack Snyder's Justice League and Supporter of Snyder Cut charitable events!
